## 2026-03-28 - No contextual token suggestions during property binding
- Added contextual scoring/ranking for bind candidates in the property binding picker
- `scoreBindCandidate()` scores tokens on 4 dimensions: primary type match (+20), value similarity via RGB distance or numeric ratio (+0-30), sibling usage — tokens already bound to same property on sibling nodes (+25), same-node context — shared path prefix with already-bound tokens (+10)
- `collectSiblingBindings()` and `collectBoundPrefixes()` helper functions gather context from rootNodes

